{"id": "art-25139", "label": "Art. 25139", "title": "Art. 25139", "slug": "art-25139", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1501423213\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1532\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1501423213\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 251<sup>39</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_223017690\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1531\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_223017690\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Fuziunea transfrontalier&#259; care a fost supus&#259;\ncontrolului de legalitate, potrivit prezentei <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:\nnormal'>legi</i>, nu poate fi <span class=SpellE>desfiin&#355;at&#259;</span>\ndup&#259; data la care aceasta produce efecte.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2020338889\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1530\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2020338889\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Prin <span class=SpellE>excep&#355;ie</span> de la\nprevederile art. 132 alin. (3), <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunea</span> în\ndeclararea <span class=SpellE>nulit&#259;&#355;ii</span> hot&#259;rârii\nadun&#259;rii generale a <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span> de aprobare\na fuziunii transfrontaliere poate fi introdus&#259; în termen de 30 de zile de\nla data public&#259;rii acesteia în Monitorul Oficial al României.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1820969593\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1529\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1820969593\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>În cadrul unei <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span> în anulare, formulate potrivit prevederilor\nart. 132 alin. (2), hot&#259;rârea adun&#259;rii generale a <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span>\nnu poate fi anulat&#259; exclusiv pentru:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1474654767\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1528\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1474654767\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)modul de stabilire a ratei de schimb a <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span>, <span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ilor</span>\nsociale sau altor titluri de valoare reprezentând capitalul social;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1947502552\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1527\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1947502552\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)modul necorespunz&#259;tor de stabilire a <span\nclass=SpellE>pre&#355;ului</span> <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span>, <span\nclass=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ilor</span> sociale sau altor titluri de valoare\nreprezentând capitalul social ale <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span> în\ncazul retragerii din societate;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1783202947\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1526\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1783202947\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)nerespectarea <span class=SpellE>cerin&#355;elor</span>\nprivind informarea <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span> asupra <span\nclass=SpellE>pre&#355;ului</span> <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span>, <span\nclass=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ilor</span> sociale sau altor titluri de valoare\nreprezentând capitalul social ale <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span> în\ncazul retragerii din societate sau asupra ratei de schimb a <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span>,\n<span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ilor</span> sociale sau altor titluri de\nvaloare reprezentând capitalul social.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_741049323\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1525\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_741049323\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Procedurile de anulare <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nde declarare a <span class=SpellE>nulit&#259;&#355;ii</span> nu pot fi <span\nclass=SpellE>ini&#355;iate</span> dac&#259; <span class=SpellE>situa&#355;ia</span>\na fost rectificat&#259;. Dac&#259; neregularitatea ce poate conduce la\ndeclararea <span class=SpellE>nulit&#259;&#355;ii</span> unei fuziuni poate fi\nremediat&#259;, <span class=SpellE>instan&#355;a</span> competent&#259;\nacord&#259; <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span> participante un\ntermen pentru rectificarea acesteia.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_185757191\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1524\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_185757191\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)R&#259;spunderea penal&#259; <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\n<span class=SpellE>consecin&#355;ele</span> acesteia, în cazul <span\nclass=SpellE>s&#259;vâr&#351;irii</span> unei <span class=SpellE>infrac&#355;iuni</span>\nde c&#259;tre societatea absorbit&#259;/<span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span>\nabsorbite, se vor angaja în sarcina <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nabsorbante/nou-constituite, potrivit <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>legii</i>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;text-align:center'><span style='mso-no-proof:\nyes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape id=\"Imagine_x0020_1338157137\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1523\"\n type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;\n mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1338157137\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>CAPITOLUL\nV:Transformarea transfrontalier&#259;</span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;text-align:center'><span style='mso-no-proof:\nyes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape id=\"Imagine_x0020_802921352\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1522\"\n type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;\n mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_802921352\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>SEC&#354;IUNEA\n1:Domeniul de aplicare. <span class=SpellE>Defini&#355;ie</span></span></b></p>"}